steps.instruction:
- Beat egg
- Whisk together mayo, egg, mustard, Worcestershire sauce, and hot sauce
- Put crab meat into a bowl
- Coarsely crush the saltines over crab meat
- Pour mayo mixture over crab meat
- Gently fold ingredients together
- Chill for at least 1 hour
- Form into 8 packed mounds
- Saute in the canola oil on medium high heat in large saute pan
- Drain on paper towel
